title: Add support for SwiftKey / SwiftKey Beta 6.2+
message:
Add support for SwiftKey / SwiftKey Beta 6.2+

- Thanks to @jaxtren at Github for pointing out that the class name had changed in latest SwiftKey updates
- The current implementation will now work for all versions of SwiftKey / SwiftKey Beta starting 6.0+ (until SwitKey developers change something drastically)

title: Add SwiftKey Keyboard 6.0+ support
message:
Add SwiftKey Keyboard 6.0+ support

New updates to SwiftKey have implemented a custom onEvaluateFullscreenMode method
instead of using the standard onEvaluateFullscreenMode method from the android
InputMethodService.

Hooking to the custom method to add support for SwiftKey Keyboard 6.0+

Signed-off-by: Shubhang Rathore <shubhang92@gmail.com>
